{"tid":2157104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"在那天輸八比二","createTime":"2020-08-14T21:32:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-15T04:51:12.000Z","uid":15954,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"dbbf647332134562ecf5d85afb669df77457a0c3","tid":2157104,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:32:40.000Z","msg":"在那天輸八比二　令巴塞迫不得已　狂炒領隊確突然<br />\n用big gay點靠得住　亂鳩走怎麼可以　任放人入涉<br />\n在大戰起用電話佬其實相當諷刺　怎努力也難明佢是憑甚麼趕走阿肚爾"},{"pid":"6cdfd617298b7cef5d9d3a6b99b4c43787d71f95","tid":2157104,"uid":15954,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T21:55:48.000Z","msg":"遇上已出走了的菲臘　一上前亂放　頻頻地做錯事"},{"pid":"3729ce268b9187e9bc39d2abd0d02027fe67301d","tid":2157104,"uid":15954,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:03:51.000Z","msg":"搞青訓到爭冠這遊戲可會預見丫　今天衰到冠軍這位置就來亦無啦<br />\n想當年目光超準　今教練變買家　淨揀三張的老野培育邊個教丫"},{"pid":"1bef477f8b1c3a6970964a4969e748a4f61e8615","tid":2157104,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:11:08.000Z","msg":"msn都要配合先有冠軍啦　叫美斯自己一個獨上腦袋有病嘛<br />\n<br />\n到慢慢熟透開始有點渣拿　終於要發威啦　你又要掛牌清走　玩野嗎"},{"pid":"cb72230aebb9742d2e077fe0e564c35c257a1b8a","tid":2157104,"uid":15954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T22:30:28.000Z","msg":"終將等到一天我們已不再「亂簽」啦　當班底革新真正大將陣容亦變化<br />\n拋低腐敗終清醒　針對弱處增兵　現今政策是完全沒有　價值留下<br />\n今天即奮起奔向球季挑戰每一家　再細閱球隊改革是否走向正軌嗎<br />\n盼日後復見當天那種光華　青訓也盡顯身價　<br />\nM&eacute;s que un club. Wake-up, Barcelona!"},{"pid":"ab35466f2d0ef19efefbf70cc08cc0944171ac8b","tid":2157104,"uid":54264,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-14T23:24:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/sFzrz4-0xiA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FsFzrz4-0xiA&d=kJyKEnCePQht%2Ftv3UrQe8fsPRfgRtgRFNgQ5kFpanIU%3D&h=034b3ee1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/sFzrz4-0xiA</a>"},{"pid":"d088153af6cd660a40392169e05b9170ff0f870c","tid":2157104,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a